The punch threw the female warrior far away. As she tried to get up, 
she could not totally conceal her pain.

Katya: I applaud you, Owlhawk. You do have the Wolf's soul and the 
Bear's strenght. You have bested me in this contest. We will work as 
part of the Maximals as of now.

Ragnar's towering form came next to her.

Ragnar: You are a powerful warrior, Owlhawk, and I have been thinking. 
I believe that you could serve the Maximals even better if we steep 
you in the ways of the Clans. If Katya does not agree, I will be your 
trainer. What say you?
